Class Trigonometric

  • java.lang.Object
    • javmos.components.JavmosComponent

        • javmos.components.functions.Trigonometric
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Cosine, Sine, Tangent

    public abstract class Trigonometric
extends Function
    This abstract class serves as a template for all trigonometric function objects. You cannot add any other methods nor modify the method signatures.
